HEADWORD: maned sheep
<hw>maned sheep</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A type of wild sheep
(<spn>Ammotragus lervia</spn>) of northern Africa; called also
<altname>Barbary sheep</altname> and
<altname>aoudad</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> aoudad, arui, audad, Barbary sheep, <spn>Ammotragus
lervia</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

